  I & X & I & X & Y & Y & I & I \\
  I & Z & I & I & I & Z & X & Z \\
  Z & I & I & Y & I & X & I & Y
\end{array}~.
\end{align}

An \([[8,2,2]]\) hyperbolic color code defined on the projective plane. It is a self-dual CSS code.

A stabilizer tableau for the code is given by \cite[ID 4926]{preset:qiskit}
